                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3ms3kn1p/manifest/annotation/p3",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"indent(1)\">Another thing! Could you not publish those several<lb/> =\n                    <persName>Dias</persName> letters = in <sic>Phamplet</sic> form? <sic>they</sic>\n                would sell <hi rend=\"underline\">well</hi><lb/> every traveling <add>יהודי</add> in\n                the <placeName>M. S.</placeName>\n                <sic>wuld</sic> buy one I warrant you.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">If you would try to give in your next volume of<lb/> the Occident\n                some more light reading for children, some<lb/> extracts from <add>מדרש</add>,\n                little anecdotes, little parables cc suitable<lb/> for the young, it would be some\n                improvement, &amp; lead to more<lb/> subscribers. There are a great many who do not\n                like always<lb/> grave matters or articles requiring thought &amp; study, some\n                lighter<lb/> food will sometimes be more acceptable.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Your Editions of <add>חמושים מחזרים תפילות</add> cc you will<lb/>\n                also have <sic>oportunity</sic> to sell, if you should resolve to make a<lb/>\n                Western Tour.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">About those <add>תפילות</add> you send by <persName>Mr\n                    Goldsmith</persName>\n                <placeName>NY</placeName><lb/> I never got them, neither are they with any of the\n                booksellers<lb/> here. Finally <persName>Mr Leeser</persName>, I shall be in\n                    <placeName>NY.</placeName> on or about<lb/>\n                <add>פסח</add>, &amp; should be very happy to make your personal acquaintance<lb/>\n                should you come there, you will easily find me by inquiring<lb/> after me. Please to\n                excuse my long epistle, any faults<lb/> in the writing of it, I am only a German\n                    <sic>decendant</sic> of <add>אהרן הכהן</add>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">yours respectfully</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(11)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">A Kohn</persName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3ms3kn1p/canvas/p3"
                }
              ]
